Package: orthos
Type: Package
Title: `orthos` is an R package for variance decomposition using conditional variational auto-encoders
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Panagiotis", "Papasaikas", email = "panagiotis.papasaikas@fmi.ch",
