Description:
    Decompose RNA-seq contrasts, for example obtained from a gene knock-out or
    compound treatment experiment, into unspecific and experiment-specific
    components. Original and decomposed contrasts can be queried agains a
    large database of publicly available contrasts to identify experiments
    with similar effects.
